                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="bg-purple-50 border border-purple-200 rounded-lg p-6">
                            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-purple-800 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                                üß† Mental Health Quality-of-Life Costs
                            </h4>
