                                    ‚Ä¢ Braghieri, L., Levy, R., & Makarin, A. (2022). Social media and mental health. American Economic Review.<br/>
                                    ‚Ä¢ U.S. Department of Transportation (2024). Revised guidance on valuation of statistical life.<br/>
                                    ‚Ä¢ Greenberg, P. E., et al. (2021). Economic burden of depression. Journal of Clinical Psychiatry.<br/>
                                    ‚Ä¢ CDC (2023). Youth Risk Behavior Surveillance System.<br/>
